395
00:42:58,240 --> 00:43:01,400
like the LinkedIn envy of like, "Oh, 
this person is at a different level.  

396
00:43:01,400 --> 00:43:07,400
We both went to the same grad school, so 
I got..." No, identify your superpowers,  

397
00:43:07,400 --> 00:43:12,640
